            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:04:10.761+09:00">1 Kao Tzu said, “Appetite for food and sex</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:04:23.714+09:00">are nature.2</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:04:38.891+09:00">JenC (benevolence, humaneness)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:04:50.714+09:00">is internal,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:05:05.217+09:00">not external;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:05:44.203+09:00">yia</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:05:50.18+09:00">is external,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-12a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:05:56.959+09:00">not internal.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:06:13.351+09:00">3 Mencius said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:07:20.381+09:00">“Why do you say that jenC is internal and and yiexternal?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:07:30.861+09:00">b 1 (Kao Tzu) said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:07:51.505+09:00">“It is old and I treat it as old;(i)(ii)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:33:34.954+09:00">it is not that there is elderliness in me.    it is not that it gets its elderliness from me.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:31:52.723+09:00">2 This is like: it is white and I treat it as white;(i)(ii)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:33:44.898+09:00">I follow, on the outside, its whiteness.I follow the fact that it is made white by outside factors.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:34:03.471+09:00">3 So I call it ‘external’.” .</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:34:17.479+09:00">c 1 (Mencius)said,(i)(ii)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:34:54.103+09:00">“Treating as white a horse’s whiteness is not different fromtreating as white a man’s whiteness.“A white horse’s whiteness is not different from a white man’swhiteness.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:48:25.595+09:00">2 I wonder if treating as old a horse’s elderliness</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:36:16.517+09:00">3 Moreover, do you say that it is(i) an old man who is yi, or one who treats him as old who is(i) elderliness which is yi, or treating as old which is yi?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:36:56.684+09:00">d 1 (Kao Tzu) said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:37:07.374+09:00">“If it is my younger brother, I love him;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:49:39.699+09:00">if it is a Ch’in man’s younger brother, I do not.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:37:28.686+09:00">2 (i) In this case, I am the one who is pleased.(ii) This is to take pleasure in myself.(iii) In this case, the motivating factor lies in me.(iv) In this,case, the explanation lies in me.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:44:32.708+09:00">2 (i) In this case, I am the one who is pleased.(ii) This is to take pleasure in myself.(iii) In this case, the motivating factor lies in me.(iv) In this,case, the explanation lies in me.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:45:20.005+09:00">I treat as old an old man from the Ch’u people;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:53:11.753+09:00">I also treat as old an old man from my (family).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:49:16.577+09:00">is not different from treating as old a man ’s elderliness?(ii) an old horse’s elderliniss is not different from an old man’selderliness?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-15a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:52:26.617+09:00">4 (i) In this case, the old men are the ones who are pleased.”(ii) This is to take pleasure in elderliness (or: the old men).”(iii) In this case, the motivating factor lies in elderliness (or: the old men).”(iv) In this case, the explanation lies in elderliness (or: the old men).”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:54:03.753+09:00">(Mencius) said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:54:57.008+09:00">“My liking a Ch’in man’s roast</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-16a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:55:13.055+09:00"> is not different frommy liking my own roast.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-16a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:55:18.796+09:00">2 Even with mere things there are such cases;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-17a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:57:03.307+09:00">so, is there also externalityin liking a roast?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:58:29.748+09:00">6A5a 1 Meng Chi-tzu asked Kungitu Tzu,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-18a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:58:57.941+09:00">“Why do you say that yia is internal?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:59:10.807+09:00">2 (Kung-tu Tzu) said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:59:21.221+09:00">“I enact my respect.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:59:32.234+09:00">That is why I say it is internal.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T20:59:50.274+09:00">b 1 (Meng Chi-tzu said,) “if a man from your village is a year older thanyour elder brother,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:00:00.824+09:00">whom do you respect?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-20a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:00:43.337+09:00">(Kungtzu Tzu) said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-21a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:00:55.013+09:00">“I respect my elder brother.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-21a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:01:06.532+09:00">2 (Meng Chi-tzu said,) “In filling their cups with wine, whom do yougive precedence to?”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:03:31.685+09:00">(Kung-tu Tzu) said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-23a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:07:30.524+09:00">3 (Meng Chi-tzu said,) “The one you respect is this;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-23a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:31:25.676+09:00">the one you treat as old is that.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-23a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:07:45.204+09:00">4 So, after all, it is on the outside,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-24a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:07:50.053+09:00">not from the inside.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-24a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:08:01.192+09:00">5 Kung-tu Tzu was unable to reply,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-24a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:08:14.037+09:00">and told Mencius about this.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:08:34.084+09:00">c 1 Mencius said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:08:47.047+09:00">“(Ask him,) ‘Do you respect your uncle,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:08:53.025+09:00">or youryounger brother?’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:09:01.531+09:00">He will say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:09:08.145+09:00">‘I respect my uncle.’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:09:43.567+09:00">2 Say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:09:55.779+09:00">‘If your younger brother is impersonating a dead ancestor at asacrifice,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:10:02.893+09:00">whom do you respect?’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:10:10.926+09:00">He will say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:10:18.434+09:00">‘I respect my youngerbrother.’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:10:44.542+09:00">3 You say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:10:56.369+09:00">‘Where then is your respect for your uncle?’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:11:05.712+09:00">He will say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:11:14.103+09:00">‘It is because of the position my younger brother occupies.’</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:11:46.326+09:00">4 You likewise say,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:12:28.631+09:00">‘(In the case of the man from my village,) it is because of the position he occupies.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-25a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:12:38.586+09:00">Ordinarily,my respect isrendered to my elder brother;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-26a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:12:44.523+09:00">on occasion, it is rendered temporarilyto the man from my village.’ ”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-26a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:12:52.765+09:00">d 1 (Meng) Chi-tzu heard this, and said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-26a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:13:07.036+09:00">“When you respect your uncle,it is respect,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-26a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:14:01.121+09:00">when you respect your younger brother, it is (also)respect.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-26a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:14:20.945+09:00">2 So, after all, it is on the outside,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-27a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:14:35.742+09:00">not from the inside.”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-27a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:15:04.509+09:00">e 1 Kung-tu Tzu said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-27a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:15:14.849+09:00">“In winter one drinks broth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-27a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:15:19.503+09:00">in summer one drinks water.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0001_tls_011-28a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-02-17T21:15:21.057+09:00">2 Does that show that even drinking and eating are on the outside?”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
